graph TD
    %% Entry Point
    Landing[Landing Page /]
    
    %% Auth Flow
    Landing -->|Click Login/Register| Auth[Auth Page /auth]
    Auth -->|Login Success| Router{Check User Role}
    
    %% Direct Access if Logged In
    Landing -->|Already Logged In| Router
    
    %% Role Based Routing
    Router -->|Consumer| ConsumerDash[Consumer Dashboard /app]
    Router -->|Manufacturer| ManufPortal[Manufacturer Portal /manufacturer]
    
    %% Consumer Actions
    ConsumerDash -->|Scan QR| Verify[Verify Page /verify]
    Verify -->|Fake/Invalid| NotVerified[Not Verified Page /not-verified]
    
    %% Manufacturer Actions
    ManufPortal --> ManufDash[Dashboard Overview]
    ManufPortal --> Medicines[My Medicines List]
    Medicines -->|Add New| Create[Create Medicine / Mint NFT]
    ManufPortal --> GenQR[Generate QR Codes]
    ManufPortal --> Reports[View Reports]
